## Data Sources Explained

| Table | Populated By | Contains |
|---|---|---|
| `AICostData_CL` | Ingestion script (Step 5) | Billed cost, tokens, model, project, direction per day |
| `AzureDiagnostics` | Diagnostic settings (Steps 1-2) | Per-request logs: latency, status, operation, errors |
| `AzureMetrics` | Diagnostic settings (Steps 1-2) | Platform metrics: TokenTransaction, ProcessedPromptTokens, AzureOpenAIRequests |

> **Project mapping note:** The Cost Management API does NOT return project-level data directly. The `Project` field in `AICostData_CL` is derived by the ingestion script via an ARM API call to list projects under each account. Single-project accounts get direct attribution; multi-project accounts are labelled as "(shared)".

